  "description": "Over the years, countless powerful cultivators have come and gone. \nBut the world never realized that behind every powerful cultivator, there seemed to be a mysterious... Dark Crow. After the Dark Crow guided a legion of young cultivators to the peak of cultivation and established their own sects, he chose to leave the world behind.\n<br><br>\nThousands of years have passed since his departure, and the once mighty sects have become weak and in danger of failing. Finally the Dark Crow returned in the form of a young man, here to fulfill his promise to defend the sects.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Tencent, translated)",
